### Vertically Centered

```
<div class='flex-row vertically-centered border-dashed-darkgray'>
 <div class='border-darkgray flex-example ex-1'>
    Element One
 </div>
 <div class='border-darkgray flex-example ex-2'>
    Element Two
 </div>
 <div class='border-darkgray flex-example ex-3'>
    Element Three
 </div>
</div>
@css {
    .flex-example {
        min-width: 225px;
        text-align: center;
    }
    .ex-1 {
        height: 40px;
    }
    .ex-2 {
        height: 23px;
    }
    .ex-3 {
        height: 76px;
    }
    .flex-row {
        height: 100px;
    }
}
```
